title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You turn the tables when you decide to take charge. You can retrieve control that you recently gave away to someone in your inner circle. You may grow aware of the ways you shrink yourself to accommodate a partner or loved one who takes up significant space in your life and mind. Thankfully, the cosmos delivers a soulful reminder today that your boundaries really do matter. Maintaining clarity about your identity and your true purpose is of the highest importance. Lao Tzu wrote, Mastering others is strength. Mastering yourself is true power. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
